 Initialize Terraform.
      $terraform init
      
 Plan for Terraform.
      $terrraform plan -out=tfplan
      
 Create an instance.
      $terraform apply tfpan
      
 Check the state of the instance.
      $terraform show
     
 Connecting to the instnace
      $gcloud sql connect name --user=name
      
 Deleting the instance
      $terraform destroy
  
  Checkinng the status again after deletion 
        $terraform show

To validate
      $terraform validate

Connecting to the instance
      $ gcloud sql connect name --user=name --quiet
